---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Discover Land Rover Experience Granville" description="The home of Land Rover, located at the heart of our world class manufacturing facility.">
	<section class="relative">
		<div class="relative h-[60vh] sm:h-[70vh] lg:h-[75vh]">
			<img src="/images/TY_Exp_Solihull_Def_04_16x9.webp" alt="Granville landscape" class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover" />
			<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/30"></div>
			<div class="relative z-10 h-full">
				<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 h-full flex items-center">
					<div class="bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-sm text-gray-900 p-6 sm:p-8 max-w-xl">
						<h1 class="lr-hero-title">
							Discover Land Rover Experience Granville
						</h1>
						<p class="lr-hero-subtitle">
							THE HOME OF LAND ROVER, LOCATED AT THE HEART OF OUR WORLD CLASS MANUFACTURING FACILITY
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section id="experiences" class="py-10 sm:py-16">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Driving Experiences</h2>
			<div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
				<div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6">
					<img src="/images/experience.jpg" alt="Driving experience" class="w-full h-40 sm:h-44 object-cover rounded-lg mb-4" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
					<h3 class="text-base font-semibold tracking-wide">Granville Taster Drive Experience</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-gray-900 text-sm leading-snug font-bold">£ 160 (Up to 2 drivers) | 1 hour</p>
					<p class="lr-body-copy">For guests who want to get behind the wheel, the One Hour Taster Drive delivers an introduction to Land Rover vehicles and off-road driving skill.</p>
					<p class="lr-body-copy">Bring a friend to enjoy the experience with you.</p>
					<a href="#booking" class="mt-3 btn-lr text-xs px-4 py-2">Book your Taster Drive</a>
				</div>
				<div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6">
					<img src="/images/experience.jpg" alt="Driving experience" class="w-full h-40 sm:h-44 object-cover rounded-lg mb-4" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
					<h3 class="text-base font-semibold tracking-wide">Granville Half Day Experience</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-gray-900 text-sm leading-snug font-bold">£ 370 (Up to 3 drivers) | 3 hours</p>
					<p class="lr-body-copy">Steep inclines, daring descents, muddy side slopes, wild streams and rock crawls; you’ll learn to conquer them in three hours of adventure through the nerve testing Jungle and Land tracks of Solihull.</p>
					<a href="#booking" class="mt-3 btn-lr text-xs px-4 py-2">Book your Half Day Drive</a>
				</div>
				<div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6">
					<img src="/images/experience.jpg" alt="Driving experience" class="w-full h-40 sm:h-44 object-cover rounded-lg mb-4" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
					<h3 class="text-base font-semibold tracking-wide">Granville Full Day Experience</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-gray-900 text-sm leading-snug font-bold">£ 650 (Up to 3 drivers) | 7 hours including lunch</p>
					<p class="lr-body-copy">Explore more challenging terrain and longer behind the wheel with this unforgettable 7-hour adventure. Navigate diverse off road elements with a qualified instructor by your side as you master the terrain that will prepare you for real world adventures.</p>
					<a href="#booking" class="mt-3 btn-lr text-xs px-4 py-2">Book your Full Day Drive</a>
				</div>
				<div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6">
					<img src="/images/experience.jpg" alt="Young off-roader" class="w-full h-40 sm:h-44 object-cover rounded-lg mb-4" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
					<h3 class="text-base font-semibold tracking-wide">Solihull Young Off-Roader Experience</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-gray-900 text-sm leading-snug font-bold">£ 160 (Up to 2 junior drivers) | 1 hour</p>
					<p class="lr-body-copy">Do you know a young person with an appetite for adventure? Get them stuck in with a Land Rover Experience. Geared to give 11-17 year olds an introduction to what it’s really like to be behind the wheel of our world-famous vehicles, it’s a safe, instructor-led experience that both educates and provides all-terrain thrills.</p>
					<a href="#booking" class="mt-3 btn-lr text-xs px-4 py-2">Book your Young Off-Roader Drive</a>
				</div>
				<div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6">
					<img src="/images/experience.jpg" alt="New owner" class="w-full h-40 sm:h-44 object-cover rounded-lg mb-4" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
					<h3 class="text-base font-semibold tracking-wide">New Owner Experience</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-gray-900 text-sm leading-snug font-bold">3 hours</p>
					<p class="lr-body-copy">As a new Land Rover owner, we invite you to experience what your vehicle has to offer with a complimentary 3-hour, off-road driving adventure in your choice of the latest Land Rover models.</p>
					<a href="#booking" class="mt-3 btn-lr text-xs px-4 py-2">Reserve your space</a>
				</div>
				<div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6">
					<img src="/images/experience.jpg" alt="Heritage Half Day" class="w-full h-40 sm:h-44 object-cover rounded-lg mb-4" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
					<h3 class="text-base font-semibold tracking-wide">Heritage Half Day Experience</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-gray-900 text-sm leading-snug font-bold">Price per vehicle: $1,325</p>
					<p class="lr-body-copy">Explore, drive off-road, and have photographic memories with the Land Rover family including the iconic Defender 90, Range Rover, and Discovery. Explore the heritage and evolution of Land Rover and stunning views of the Santa Lucia mountains.</p>
					<a href="#booking" class="mt-3 btn-lr text-xs px-4 py-2">Book now</a>
				</div>
				<div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6">
					<img src="/images/experience.jpg" alt="Heritage Full Day" class="w-full h-40 sm:h-44 object-cover rounded-lg mb-4" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
					<h3 class="text-base font-semibold tracking-wide">Heritage Full Day Experience</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-gray-900 text-sm leading-snug font-bold">Price per vehicle: $1,650</p>
					<p class="lr-body-copy">Experience the evolution of Land Rover. Drive and explore all the Land Rover families including the iconic Land Rover Defender 90, modern Range Rover and Discovery vehicle on an off-road trail with an expert instructor while navigating obstacles and varying terrain with a beautiful backdrop. Lunch is also included.</p>
					<a href="#booking" class="mt-3 btn-lr text-xs px-4 py-2">Book now</a>
				</div>
				<div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6">
					<img src="/images/experience.jpg" alt="Advanced Programs" class="w-full h-40 sm:h-44 object-cover rounded-lg mb-4" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
					<h3 class="text-base font-semibold tracking-wide">Advanced Programs</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-gray-900 text-sm leading-snug font-bold">Price per vehicle: Starts at $1350</p>
					<p class="lr-body-copy">We offer several Advanced Programs including Recovery, Winching, Bespoke, and much more. We are also able to tailor programs to fit your needs. Call us for additional information.</p>
					<a href="#booking" class="mt-3 btn-lr text-xs px-4 py-2">Contact us</a>
				</div>
				<div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6">
					<img src="/images/experience.jpg" alt="Owner's Days" class="w-full h-40 sm:h-44 object-cover rounded-lg mb-4" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
					<h3 class="text-base font-semibold tracking-wide">Owner's Days</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-gray-900 text-sm leading-snug font-bold">Price per owner's vehicle: $495</p>
					<p class="lr-body-copy">Throughout the year, we're proud to feature exclusive Owner's Day events at Land Rover Experience California. Unique from typical Experience Center experiences, at these events owners bring and drive their own vehicle, and spend the day with other Land Rover owners.</p>
					<a href="#booking" class="mt-3 btn-lr text-xs px-4 py-2">Book now</a>
				</div>
				<div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6">
					<img src="/images/experience.jpg" alt="Groups" class="w-full h-40 sm:h-44 object-cover rounded-lg mb-4" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
					<h3 class="text-base font-semibold tracking-wide">Groups</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-gray-900 text-sm leading-snug font-bold">Pricing Per Person: $220 and up or Contact Us</p>
					<p class="lr-body-copy">Create unforgettable experiences to fit your group needs. Our experiences are ideal for corporate outings, team building, special occasions, friends, families, and everything in between. Since our experiences are custom, pricing may vary.</p>
					<a href="#booking" class="mt-3 btn-lr text-xs px-4 py-2">Contact us</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section id="factory" class="py-10 sm:py-16 bg-gray-50">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Factory Tour Experiences</h2>
			<div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
				<div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6">
					<img src="/images/TY_Exp_JLRFactoryTour_10_16x9.webp" alt="Factory tour" class="w-full h-40 sm:h-44 object-cover rounded-lg mb-4" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
					<h3 class="text-base font-semibold tracking-wide">Granville Factory Tour</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-gray-900 text-sm leading-snug font-bold">£50 (Per adult) | 3 hours</p>
					<p class="lr-body-copy">Guided tour of our state‑of‑the‑art production facility. See how iconic Jaguar and Land Rover vehicles are brought to life.</p>
					<a href="#booking" class="mt-3 btn-lr text-xs px-4 py-2">Book your Factory Tour</a>
				</div>
				<div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6">
					<img src="/images/TY_Exp_JLRFactoryTour_10_16x9.webp" alt="Factory tour" class="w-full h-40 sm:h-44 object-cover rounded-lg mb-4" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
					<h3 class="text-base font-semibold tracking-wide">Granville VIP Experience</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-gray-900 text-sm leading-snug font-bold">£400 (For up to 2 guests) | 3 hours</p>
					<p class="lr-body-copy">Concierge welcome and chauffeured access to premium production areas, including paint shop and Trim & Final, plus refreshments.</p>
					<a href="#booking" class="mt-3 btn-lr text-xs px-4 py-2">Book your VIP Experience</a>
				</div>
				<div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6">
					<img src="/images/TY_Exp_JLRFactoryTour_10_16x9.webp" alt="Factory tour" class="w-full h-40 sm:h-44 object-cover rounded-lg mb-4" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
					<h3 class="text-base font-semibold tracking-wide">Granville Configuration Experience</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-gray-900 text-sm leading-snug font-bold">£400 (For up to 2 guests) | 3 hours</p>
					<p class="lr-body-copy">One‑to‑one session with experts to craft your bespoke vehicle. Includes privileged access to key production areas.</p>
					<a href="#booking" class="mt-3 btn-lr text-xs px-4 py-2">Book your Configuration Experience</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section id="testimonial" class="py-10 sm:py-16">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4">
			<blockquote class="lr-quote">
				“ What a fantastic day. My instructor, Jo, was a joy and incredibly knowledgeable. This was my first off road experience and I learnt so much. The Defender was great to drive and nothing was stopping it. I would absolutely recommend this to anyone interested in cars or motoring heritage. ”
			</blockquote>
			<p class="lr-quote-author">Terry, Desford — Review taken from TripAdvisor</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section id="contact" class="py-10 sm:py-16 bg-gray-50">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<p class="mt-3 lr-contact-copy text-gray-900">Have a question about Land Rover Experience Granville? We look forward to hearing from you.</p>
			<div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8">
				<div>
					<ul class="space-y-3 lr-contact-copy">
						<li><strong>Email:</strong> <a class="text-[#004b2d] hover:underline" href="mailto:info@example.com">info@example.com</a></li>
						<li><strong>Phone:</strong> <a class="text-[#004b2d] hover:underline" href="tel:+10000000000">(000) 000‑0000</a></li>
					</ul>
					<div class="mt-6 flex justify-center">
						<a href="#" class="btn-dark btn-dark-lg">Get In Touch</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
